Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.72,0:00:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're late, damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.22,0:00:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Here they are!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.47,0:00:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Awful! This is awful!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.42,0:00:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Fukuike and the\Nother teachers are in the area. {wandering around}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.42,0:00:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're spotted, they'll suspend us all \Nfor breaking the school rules!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.27,0:00:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, scatter, people! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.93,0:00:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, for you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.17,0:00:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, skedaddle! {hurry}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.18,0:00:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Fukuike!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.87,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.07,0:00:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're off! {went}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.61,0:00:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it worked.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, getting them alone together \Nreally takes some doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.36,0:00:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're together all year \Nand still haven't even made it to their first kiss.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's no Fukuike anywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.18,0:00:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.38,0:01:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys all doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.53,0:01:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No... we, uh... were just... {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.84,0:01:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kuroiwa and the others decided to take you\Nup on that thing you were recruiting for earlier. {not sure if she's talking to kuroiwa or fukuike, but essentially she means "remember that thing sensei was recruiting for earlier? well, kuroiwa-tachi are going there now"}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The official English training camp? {????? says it with some stupid lisp}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.80,0:01:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.81,0:01:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We just came to see them off.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.14,0:01:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, I see. And here I thought not a single applicant would show! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.03,0:01:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As the person in charge, I'd be screwed!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.04,0:01:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sensei. Vice Principal!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.65,0:01:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Manami and the others are okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.04,0:01:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shimizu, after all. \NThey'll pull through somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.04,0:01:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, a trip with just the\Ntwo of us sounds pretty stylish, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.75,0:02:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! {yabai?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.68,0:02:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.89,0:02:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Perfect weather for the beach, isn't it? {/day for swimming}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.43,0:02:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, since we're going there anyway, \Nshould we stay over? {????? can't hear shit}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.99,0:02:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you told your parents \Nit was a day trip, didn't you? {you'll return in the evening}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.33,0:02:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. I can say that \Nas many times as I want. Right? {??? meaning "I can tell them it's a day trip every day" ig?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.17,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Not on the train... {here/this kind of place}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.15,Top,,0,0,0,,Machida, Machida Station.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.25,0:03:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'll go grab some juice and bentos.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so chilly! {cool in here}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,True! I feel rejuvenated. {it brings you back to life}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.87,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't buy them in time. {probs "missed my opportunity to..."}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot!\NI made sandwiches already.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, I'm drenched in sweat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,True. I feel so gross.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we change?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, so bold! {daitai?}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.99,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. \NSaori's right here!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Found them!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,I-It got caught in the zipper!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.97,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If this turned into spending the night \Nwith Saori, that'd be the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.52,0:04:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Manami and Yuki \Nhaven't returned home yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.03,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they get caught by Fukuike-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.84,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.66,0:04:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I just meant being alone together \Nis kind of nice, and all that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.80,0:04:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not thinking anything weird, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of weird? {prompting her to say it herself, exposing her as weird instead of him}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.06,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.06,0:04:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,At last! The blazing sun, \Nthe sea breeze filling our chests...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,That sea breeze is nice... {??? ano ko? aruku? waruku?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew!{that hurt}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The guy's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, give me a hand. {help me get up ig? maybe to pull the girl up?}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.18,0:05:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My contact lens slipped behind my eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.36,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was awfully close. \NYou heard the train coming, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.42,0:05:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I was too focused \Non looking for my contacts.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.81,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's back.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.68,0:06:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of it, I end up falling all the time. {foot slips}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this one's from the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from five days ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one's from a week ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.86,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then? {what's next}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.50,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from ten days—no, eleven... \NMaybe even two weeks ago?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.43,0:06:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So we ultimately went\Nto check up on them, huh? {speaking half to the audience}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.39,0:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Think those two are making \Nany progress right about now? {things going well}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Principal, look.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This car's almost empty.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.16,0:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Looks like a good place \Nto teach the fundamentals. {of kendo fencing ig? that's why they need space?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think about that girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.62,0:06:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly? I'm creeped out by her. \NShe's gloomy! And hard to read! {hard to figure out; elusive; slippery; vague; subtle}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We sure picked up a weird tag-along.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.15,0:06:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you really think \Nshe just fell on the track by accident? {lit: her foot slipped - but that was clearly more than that, so yeah she probably meant "falling"}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it didn't seem like that at all. {/back then, I was sure she does it on purpose}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? There's too much that bothers me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the bandage on her left wrist?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.08,0:07:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but…
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way, you mean this? {wrist slitting}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.11,0:07:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And those fresh wounds—aren't they\Nhesitation scars from failing over and over? {trying}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Saori...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.79,0:07:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's taking a long time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't she only go to the restroom to change? {clothes}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! You think she jumped? {to her death}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.49,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I dropped it again. {this time}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.70,0:07:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, aren't you hungry? \NWould you like a sandwich?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.01,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandwiches feel kind of lonely.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.88,0:07:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about some fruit?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.99,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.85,0:07:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got this, \Nbut not the can opener.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.64,0:08:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.80,0:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.17,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, if this works, how about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Th-This"?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't open a can with that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.65,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You take the knife away from her. Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a godsend!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really. You saved us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, don't hesitate and let me have that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.97,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, this is a little too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.41,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's buy frozen oranges \Nat the next station, right? {mandarins}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Good idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.43,0:08:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly felt overwhelmed by sadness.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That medicine just now, wasn't it...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.77,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am in the way, aren't I? {third wheel}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.54,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course not! \NThe more the merrier, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.02,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having loads of fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.81,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange, I thought we got off together. {but can't find her now}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should ask a policeman \Nto walk her back or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just enjoy the beach alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.51,0:09:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave it at that! First it was\Nthe knife, and now it's the rope and pills!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be wandering around now, \Nlooking for a place to die.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, much ado about nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun, you jerk!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are sensitive, you know! {easy to hurt}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you just leave her at that \Nif that were me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Idiot! Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you've been so cold to her!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That must've pushed her over the limit! {??? maybe "we should always be careful around her"}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.69,0:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she's gone already, \Nthere's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! You really don't have \Na shred of sensitivity, do you? {delicacy}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.93,0:10:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at this! This is Kojima Island—\Napparently it's famous for its love knots.{since anctient times}{marriage; marriage tie; love knot}{kojima may just be "small island"}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.58,0:10:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right by the beach we're going to!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, why so cold? {lit: you say is that so...}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.34,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… would you like any of this?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You…
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought enough for you two as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.64,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly got my appetite back.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because I met you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, sure! We'll take it, won't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, give it here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.32,0:11:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about Kojima Island too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.13,0:11:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.94,0:11:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If a couple stands on that historic cliff, \Nthey become blessed by the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.47,0:11:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You two might benefit from it. {lit: you might be a good match - not sure what she means, probably that they're a couple and that means they should go there and receive the blessing, not that they're a good match for each other}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-Yeah, it's just the thing for us! {match}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting! {yarashi?}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go there too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I don't know yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.09,0:11:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the shape of that \Nlone pine tree's branches is amazing. {for hanging yourself}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.03,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also a great spot for diving... \Nif you don't mind the rocks below, that is.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.62,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, if it's something you're into, \Nwould you wanna swim with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of our fun-loving friends \Nwill be joining us soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.11,0:11:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.09,0:11:53.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.79,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's okay! \NRight, Yuji-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You bet!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This stuff is great! \NI can't stop eating it! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.63,0:12:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.97,0:12:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{maybe "ugh"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.74,0:12:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun! I'm going to change now, but you—\Ndon't take your eyes off that girl, got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.08,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll go all the way \Nwith your boundless compassion. {humanity/benevolence}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get all stubborn about it. {lit: be a contrarian}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.89,0:12:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she gets her energy and brightness back, \Nwe'll have some time all to ourselves, okay? {have sex}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.86,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-a-lly! {ho n to}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{????? maybe "success" or something}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Sakazaki-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Akimoto-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you follow me all this way?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you adorable?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.37,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I mean... excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.67,0:13:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, Sakazaki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.42,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be shy!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not! {???????? tetsudaimasu? doesn't make sense}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.87,0:13:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.37,0:13:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here again this year! \NThe Seaside Madonna Contest!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will claim the title of our New Madonna?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, contestant number one, step right up!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It really worked!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, I'm falling!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an accident! {???? icchatta?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped my contacts!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.86,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez... Where are you looking?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.81,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly why \NI begged you to watch her!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's disappeared again!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.62,0:14:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What if something happens to her?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.76,0:14:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally talked her out of it  \Nand were just becoming friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find her, no matter what.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, doesn't ring a bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't see her.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.31,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That lady said she went this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's her! What do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.14,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori, go get help!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.10,0:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful…
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.31,0:15:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah!}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think Saori and Yuji are?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.81,0:15:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in the middle of the {\i1}action,{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}I imagine. {having fun}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori, I want all of you... {does this need quotation marks?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.84,0:15:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've treasured myself until today, \Nonly for you, Yuji-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.21,0:16:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, not there!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.70,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, are we two really \N{\i1}that{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}corrupted by his influence? {vulgar; indecent - not sure if she means this or "look indecent from the outside"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.89,0:16:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then I'm going \Nto find myself a fancy guy too!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Someone!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone come!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.89,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami! Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.80,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji went to Kojima Island \Nto stop a suicidal girl! {/from throwing oneself (e.g. into the water to commit suicide)}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.98,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.51,0:16:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.43,0:16:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When a girl wants to die in a beautiful place,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.21,0:16:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,she always believes a wonderful prince \Nwill come to stop her.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.46,0:16:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I bet she thinks that until\NYuji comes to save her, she can't die.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And if anything,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.07,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd rather they both go together.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.07,0:16:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.93,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that—you'll jinx it! {lit: unlucky/ill omened things}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.50,0:16:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's an earthquake!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I-It's a big one!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's over.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.50,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Tsunami warning issued!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.57,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Everyone on the beach, evacuate immediately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My, it's you girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.37,0:17:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuate now! \NWhat if this tsunami hits?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.33,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Akimoto-sensei! \NWhat a coincidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here, Fukuike-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And the vice principal too?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Help save Yuji-kun, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.12,0:17:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission to save Sakazaki \Nis proceeding in perfect order! {perfectly ordered; perfectly coordinated}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One-two-three, this is the Yamagawa Style! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.58,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jouka's trademark strategy! {????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.14,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}I repeat:{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.91,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Everyone on the beach, \Nplease evacuate immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.91,0:18:19.87,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}The earthquake has subsided, but a tsunami has occurred! This is not a drill! {\i0}{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.10,0:18:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't do it! {?? yosanei ka?}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.89,0:18:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop me. \NI finally found the perfect place.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Don't do anything rash! {don't be hasty}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.31,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.68,0:18:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're doing something stupid, stop! {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.92,0:19:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.75,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... I'm saved!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.20,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't grab me there, geez! {in weird places}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere else to grab!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.94,0:19:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.53,0:19:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Couples who get splashed by the high waves \N on this cliff are destined to never again be apart. {https://jisho.org/word/%E5%A5%91%E3%82%8A - dunno how to convey all of those meanings in en. Me neither - Paul}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.96,0:20:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun, hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Saori! Thank God you're safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.88,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.58,0:21:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? \NPlease stay with us!
Comment: 10,0:24:41.91,0:24:44.91,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.54,0:12:12.63,Song,,0,0,0,,{song is 土曜日のアマン; got full lyrics from EB's booklet}{抱いて抱いて抱いて抱きしめて} Hold me, hold me, hold me tight,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.63,0:12:19.14,Song,,0,0,0,,{朝の光に包まれて}wrapped in the morning light
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.14,0:12:25.77,Song,,0,0,0,,{燃えて燃えて熱い腕の中で}Burning, burning, in these heated arms,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.77,0:12:32.86,Song,,0,0,0,,{踊り上手な ジルバのよう}like a nimble jive dancer
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.41,0:12:45.87,Song,,0,0,0,,{ほほえみで やさしい愛を感じて}Feeling gentle love through a smile,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.88,0:12:52.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{きらびやかにしなやかに踊ってゆく}shimmering, supple, we dance on
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.79,0:12:59.60,Song,,0,0,0,,{あなたの愛と私の愛が}Your love and my love
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.60,0:13:04.74,Song,,0,0,0,,{溶けあいながら まぶしいくらい}melting together, dazzling bright
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.91,0:13:13.27,Song,,0,0,0,,{そして幸せを求めあいいついつまでも }And seeking happiness forever and ever...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.26,0:21:22.87,Song,,0,0,0,,{そっと愛して; got full lyrics from EB's booklet: そっと愛して気づかれないで\N素早く部屋の灯りを消して\N街はもう夢のさなか\N合鍵はミルクボックスの中\Nそっと愛してさざ波のよう\N小さな高なりただくりかえし\N手探りのホラ熱い胸は\N過ぎて行く真夏の匂い\Nプリーズ ぬくもりを\Nプリーズ さりげなく\N哀しみに変えないで\N秘密のまま愛して\Nだけどくちびるふれるたびに\N汗ばむ心はじけるの\N青い月の光道しるべに\N足音は駅に棄ててきて\Nそっと愛して傷つけないで\Nあなたのことを教えないで\N目覚まし時計鳴るまでには\Nもう少し時間があるわ\Nブリーズ ときめきを\Nプリーズ ゆっくりと\N今は吐息を数えながら\N幸せ感じていたいだけ\N蒼い月の光道しるべに\N運命も駅に棄ててきて\Nやましさにかえないで\N私よりも愛して\Nプリーズ\Nブリーズ\Nぬくもりを\Nさりげなく\N哀しみに変えないで\N秘密のまま愛して\Nだけどくちびるふれるたびに\N汗ばむ心はじけるの\N蒼い月の光道しるべに\N足音は駅に棄ててきて\Nそしてもっとそっと愛して\N気付かれないで\Nだからもっと そっと愛して\N気付かれないで\Nそっと愛して}Love me gently, without being noticed
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.87,0:21:27.31,Song,,0,0,0,,Quickly turn off the light in the room
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.31,0:21:31.63,Song,,0,0,0,,The city is already deep in dreams,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:31.63,0:21:36.02,Song,,0,0,0,,and the spare key is in the milk box
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.02,0:21:40.45,Song,,0,0,0,,Love me softly, like rippling waves,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.45,0:21:44.93,Song,,0,0,0,,a small throbbing, repeating
Dialogue: 5,0:21:44.93,0:21:49.31,Song,,0,0,0,,Feeling our way, these hot hearts,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.31,0:21:53.52,Song,,0,0,0,,the scent of passing midsummer
Dialogue: 5,0:21:54.41,0:22:03.31,Song,,0,0,0,,Please, don't turn warmth into sorrow
Dialogue: 5,0:22:03.31,0:22:13.85,Song,,0,0,0,,Please, casually, love me in secret
Dialogue: 5,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.87,Song,,0,0,0,,{それゆけMY HEART! by Tom Cat - marty couldn't even find past auctions for it and no trace of lyrics on the internet; translating by ear} Go for it, my heart! {soreyuke - there you go etc}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.93,0:22:46.92,Song,,0,0,0,,A happy-sounding conversation,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.92,0:22:54.94,Song,,0,0,0,,pushing through at last, the waiting ends—\Nan aggressive style that makes everyone turn {???}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.36,0:23:00.82,Song,,0,0,0,,Walking around all flashy,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:00.82,0:23:04.50,Song,,0,0,0,,but when your heart really hurts,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:04.50,0:23:09.64,Song,,0,0,0,,that's one more beat added
Dialogue: 5,0:23:11.62,0:23:18.46,Song,,0,0,0,,An airhead like me—hurt, but it can't be helped
Dialogue: 5,0:23:18.46,0:23:21.84,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me about human ambitions,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:21.84,0:23:27.07,Song,,0,0,0,,just start moving your body like a fool and DANCE! {???}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.14,0:23:30.87,Song,,0,0,0,,Dancin' on the street
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.87,0:23:32.82,Song,,0,0,0,,My playful heart
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.58,Song,,0,0,0,,DANCE!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.31,0:23:38.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Dancin' on the street
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.98,Song,,0,0,0,,My extreme heart
Dialogue: 5,0:23:39.98,0:23:41.75,Song,,0,0,0,,DANCE!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:42.32,0:23:44.78,Song,,0,0,0,,Dancin' on the street
Dialogue: 5,0:23:44.78,0:23:47.14,Song,,0,0,0,,My precious heart {???}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.14,0:23:48.79,Song,,0,0,0,,DANCE!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:49.58,0:23:52.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Dancin' on the street
Dialogue: 5,0:23:52.08,0:23:55.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Go for it, my heart!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:59.81,0:24:04.90,Song,,0,0,0,,M-M-My heart
Dialogue: 5,0:24:06.63,0:24:10.20,Song,,0,0,0,,M-M-MY HEART!
